  <brief_title>A Phase 4 Study With Tamsulosin OCAS to Assess Nighttime Voiding.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Assess the Effect of Tamsulosin OCAS 0.4 mg Tablets, Once Daily on Nocturia, Compared to Placebo, in Patients With Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms Associated With Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia</official_title>
