  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study with two treatment arms (Tamsulosin OCAS
      0.4 mg &amp; placebo). The study comprises a 2-week placebo run-in followed by a 12-week
      treatment period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
